 <h3> <a href="http://usprodoubles.com" >USProdoubles.com</a> - Your Site Will look like this. Online Today. </h3>  
  <h2 class="loud">Manage and Publish Your Tournament Online.</h2>
  
 <strong>My Tournament Online</strong> is the ideal way to run your tournament utilizing the power of the internet.  You can avoid
 all of the phone calls, and emails associated with running a tournament.  <strong>All your teams and players will have access to your custom
 built website with your schedules, draws, recent results, directions and general information!</strong> The U.S. Professional Squash Doubles Championship
 relies on My Tournament Online to keep it players and fans up to date with tournament info. Check out 
 <a href" http://usprodoubles.com">USProDoubles.com</a> to <strong>see a live tournament site in action</strong>. Your site can be up and running in less than 1 day.
</p>

<p>
  <div id="navigation">
 <h4>   <a href="//shawnlindsey.com">Upgrade to full interactive website</a>  |  <a href="/brackets">Build and print your free brackets now</a>
  </div> <!-- navigation -->
</p>

<p>
 <h3 class="loud">Have 3 Tournament Sponsors? Your Website Pays for Itself.</h3>
    
 <strong>My Tournament Online</strong> allows you to easily upload your sponsors images / ads.  Your sponsor ads will rotate on your home page (and other pages) for visitors to easily see.  Depending on what you charge for sponsoring your tournament your website can help you attract sponsors and generate revenue above and beyond your current level of sponsorship.  Your sponsors will love the quality of your website and having their business displayed. Many sites have more than <strong>tripled their sponsor dollars!</strong> Your professional site will generate your tournament more revenue, get your information out, and greatly reduce the calls and emails with the same questions your teams and players have. <a href="http://usprodoubles.com" >USProdoubles.com</a> generates enough sponsor dollars to run the tournament and pay out large cash prizes for winning teams.
</p>

<p>
 <h3 class="loud">Google Maps Integrated Into Your Directions Page.</h3>
    
Your site will have an interactive <strong>Google map embedded into the directions page</strong>.  Visitors can click on and get directions directly from home. Map works seamlessly with current smartphones so your teams and players can pull up a map while on the go.
</p>

<p>
 <h3 class="loud">Build Tournament Draws / Brackets of Any Size.</h3>
Build your draws out to any size. You can create draws as large as 1000 teams or as small as 2. Post your draw online and update or redo it at will. The easy to use administrative interface makes running your tournament online a breeze.
</p>

<p>
 <h3 class="loud">Email All Users and Fans</h3>
 Your site includes your own personal domain name (e.g. greater-valley-open.com, boston-baseball-tourny.com, joes-tournament.com) and also includes an email account for your site.  Players and website visitors can email you at tournamentdirector@YourName.com.  <strong>Within your administrative interface you can email ALL your players and users at once!</strong>
</p>
